that's all.

4
00:00:04,944 --> 00:00:06,625
<i>I need to get you</i>
into the OR immediately.

5
00:00:06,710 --> 00:00:07,641
<i>I'll do whatever
you say.</i>

6
00:00:07,726 --> 00:00:09,680
