because my OR is spotless.

8
00:00:13,007 --> 00:00:14,750
<i>This is day five
with the same mask.</i>

9
00:00:14,835 --> 00:00:17,351
I've put in an emergency order,
and it turns out

10
00:00:17,436 --> 00:00:19,033
this shipment
is on its way.

11
00:00:19,118 --> 00:00:20,859
You said
Red Rock wouldn't pay.

12
00:00:20,944 --> 00:00:22,585
They won't.
But they did.

13
00:00:22,835 --> 00:00:25,101
Don't worry,
I'm not expecting anything...

14
00:00:25,608 --> 00:00:28,414
You may now enjoy your first kiss
as husband and wife.

15
00:00:39,548 --> 00:00:41,274
I feel like we've done
the research,

16
00:00:41,359 --> 00:00:43,109
and the results
are in.

17
00:00:43,975 --> 00:00:45,883
Sex is better
when you're married.

18
00:00:47,226 --> 00:00:48,875
Was there a concern
that it wouldn't be?

19
00:00:48,960 --> 00:00:50,249
No, I just didn't think

20
00:00:50,334 --> 00:00:52,899
it could possibly get
any better, but it did.

21
00:00:53,054 --> 00:00:54,710
Nice recovery.

22
00:00:55,146 --> 00:00:56,733
We need to get going.

23
00:00:58,671 --> 00:01:00,984
Five more minutes
in the love bubble.

24
00:01:02,984 --> 00:01:04,524
Fine, five more minutes.

25
00:01:04,609 --> 00:01:06,283
But then you gotta
get your ass out of bed.

26
00:01:06,367 --> 00:01:07,383
You've got that meeting.

27
00:01:07,468 --> 00:01:08,969
♪ <i>Taste of romance</i> ♪

28
