♪ <i>Taste of romance...</i> ♪

29
00:01:11,561 --> 00:01:15,054
Had we recklessly hopped
into bed two years ago,

30
00:01:15,648 --> 00:01:17,460
who knows where
we'd be right now?

31
00:01:17,749 --> 00:01:18,821
Agreed.

32
00:01:18,906 --> 00:01:22,187
And we'll restrain ourselves
in public

33
00:01:22,374 --> 00:01:25,571
to keep this...
Whatever this is...

34
00:01:25,656 --> 00:01:27,601
Uh... private?

35
00:01:28,492 --> 00:01:29,243
Agreed.

36
00:01:29,328 --> 00:01:32,476
♪ <i>Run your fingers soft...</i> ♪

37
00:01:32,562 --> 00:01:35,484
Are you just going to agree
with everything I say?

38
00:01:36,210 --> 00:01:39,015
Please don't tell me
you're losing your edge,

39
00:01:39,210 --> 00:01:40,789
Andre Jeremiah.

40
00:01:41,103 --> 00:01:43,781
Oh, please.
Losing my edge

41
00:01:44,164 --> 00:01:48,125
is the last thing
you have to be worried about,

42
00:01:48,210 --> 00:01:49,868
Mina Okafor.

43
00:01:49,953 --> 00:01:52,499
♪ <i>The current in your head.</i> ♪

44
